# features/products.feature

Feature: Product Management

  Scenario: Reading a product by ID
    Given the following products exist:
      | name       | description        | price | stock | category   |
      | Product A  | A great product    | 100   | 10    | Electronics|
    When I view the product with ID 1
    Then I should see the product "Product A"
    And the product description should be "A great product"
    And the price should be "100"
    And the stock should be "10"
    And the category should be "Electronics"
